1040
00:56:08,920 --> 00:56:12,090
Apa itu salah?

1041
00:56:12,090 --> 00:56:14,400
Kenapa kamu memarahiku?

1042
00:56:14,400 --> 00:56:17,499
Aku menantu

1043
00:56:17,499 --> 00:56:19,529
